%%{init: {'theme':'base', 'themeVariables': { 'primaryColor': '#f4f4f4', 'edgeLabelBackground':'#ffffff', 'tertiaryColor': '#e2e8f0'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Local API
    participant Remote API
    participant ChromaDB
    
    User->>Local API: POST /search (Room Photo)
    Local API->>Remote API: POST /detect
    Remote API-->>Local API: Bounding boxes & confidence scores
    
    Local API->>Local API: Select highest-confidence crop
    
    par Parallel Inference
        Local API->>Remote API: POST /embed_b64
        Remote API-->>Local API: Visual Embedding Vector
    and
        Local API->>Remote API: POST /tag_b64
        Remote API-->>Local API: Raw Taxonomy Tags
    end
    
    Local API->>Local API: Apply Semantic Snapper to Tags
    Local API->>Local API: Build Scalar Where Filter<br/>(Color, Material, Style)
    
    Local API->>ChromaDB: Query with Filter & Embedding
    
    alt Empty Results
        Local API->>ChromaDB: Fallback Query (No Metadata Filter)
        ChromaDB-->>Local API: Results
    else Results Found
        ChromaDB-->>Local API: Results
    end
    
    Local API->>Local API: Rank by Cosine Similarity Score
    Local API-->>User: Top-K Recommendations
